{"tid":1603593,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"【 1 0 . 1 】 全民black bloc唔係淨係著件黑TEE咁簡單！","createTime":"2019-09-29T17:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T15:34:24.000Z","uid":119623,"like":133,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"aaeff4f3c3c05284591069aa074ff184f748cd9f","tid":1603593,"uid":119623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KoegX8Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKoegX8Z.png&h=3df3ac6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日見到有唔少人著得靚一靚，但而家係抗爭，唔係開party，唔該著返套舒適方便嘅衫。<br />\n<br />\n較高戰鬥力服裝：防水風褸 + 防水長褲 + 雨褸<br />\n較低戰鬥力服裝：黑TEE + 冰袖 + 黑色長褲<br />\n<br />\n記得帶返頂帽，將頭髮收好。有黑超就帶埋，口罩/包面頭巾是必須的。總之愈認唔到你就愈好。飾物可免則免。如果你會接觸到任何野，最好帶對手套。<br />\n<br />\n袋孭返個背囊，方便。散物資時又可以塞多啲。可以孭多個腰包，放貴重物品，走難時冇咁易唔見嘢。<br />\n<br />\n女仔忍忍手唔好化妝，萬一中咗嘢就會kick曬係皮膚入面，好難搞。當然可以帶啲化妝品走時變身用。<br />\n<br />\n帶多一、兩套衫換是常識吧。仲有記住攝衫喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多裝備深水埗都有得買，好聽日去入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每人順手帶多包索帶、士巴拿、六角匙等等嘅工具，到時就冇咁手足無措。<br />\n<br />\n一人一把長遮攜身，再袋多把縮骨遮。長遮畀咗人，都仲有把縮骨遮保護自己。<br />\n<br />\n有嘢要補充，歡迎留言。<br />\n<br />\n今時唔同往日，大家要萬事小心，細心留意四周，謹慎行動。為人為己，應要有充分裝備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n矛同盾互相配合，先會有好嘅發揮。<br />\n好想同大家齊上齊落⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">10 . 1 要見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQaWX9R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQaWX9R.jpg&h=ca8c60fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"169f6ee1e105dd5451c8d22ce7aa0dc5f8272dd6","tid":1603593,"uid":119623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:10:01.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"8b4cb49c8b2e05979aed061d6884a720181f4bc0","tid":1603593,"uid":119623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:10:11.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"4ee59a524898fbd1a2624c82417bce6ec5346389","tid":1603593,"uid":119623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:10:23.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"55dcaa463212b879761d4dd78627824ec7a19b07","tid":1603593,"uid":119623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:10:33.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"020ee96131d9cba8d49160af744fad285337273a","tid":1603593,"uid":119623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:10:43.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"3f673e7586b1ec5f16bc9985392c585790fd5eac","tid":1603593,"uid":119623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:10:53.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"4fd3edf44437c240d1b550abeca6b70df16b940d","tid":1603593,"uid":119623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:11:03.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"8f4bec620cf157c80d2283a7a664e03da5db6b44","tid":1603593,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:11:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0586ee0716f7ca561f70930e88def619efe60e1f","tid":1603593,"uid":7855,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:11:10.000Z","msg":"30/9 開始已經要咁著<br />\n最後每日都咁著<br />\n各位冇得驚ga la"},{"pid":"3c622678476ebc07ee32cabb2250f90c3924513a","tid":1603593,"uid":119623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:11:15.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"bb1b4a9061ed8c70b21ab352eb611b8cd7722df2","tid":1603593,"uid":119623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:11:35.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"fdb3f460334a70ea76667add13fb382df0c48e08","tid":1603593,"uid":75263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:11:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dba859dbdfba678c0ea9466e1a1993b5a157c50a","tid":1603593,"uid":119623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:11:47.000